Class PrivacyPropagator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.sysds.runtime.privacy.propagation.PrivacyPropagator

  • public class PrivacyPropagator
extends Object
    Class with static methods merging privacy constraints of operands in expressions to generate the privacy constraints of the output.

      • matrixMultiplicationPropagation

        public static PrivacyConstraint matrixMultiplicationPropagation(MatrixBlock input1,
                                                                PrivacyConstraint privacyConstraint1,
                                                                MatrixBlock input2,
                                                                PrivacyConstraint privacyConstraint2)
        Return the merged fine-grained privacy constraint of a matrix multiplication with the given privacy constraints. The current implementation has a tendency to create small ranges of privacy level private. These ranges could be merged to create fewer ranges spanning the same elements.
        Parameters:
        input1 - first input matrix block
        privacyConstraint1 - privacy constraint of the first matrix
        input2 - second input matrix block
        privacyConstraint2 - privacy constraint of the second matrix
        Returns:
        merged privacy constraint
